Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2947.3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2947.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遭遇了一场巨大的离子风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have been through a severe ion storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一名船员不幸牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One crewman is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舰体严重损坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's damage is considerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我下令飞船临时停靠在11号星际基地进行维修\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have ordered a nonscheduled layover on Starbase 11 for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有关舰体的详细损坏报告已递交给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A full report of damages was made to the commanding officer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,11号星际基地指挥官，斯通准将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of starbase 11, Commodore stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,18号维修点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maintenance Section 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们当前的工作是在为无畏号进行维修\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your section is working on the Intrepid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我重新安排你们优先维修进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reschedule. The Enterprise is on priority one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经读了3遍了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That makes three times you've read it, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有什么问题吗？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is there an error? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但有船员牺牲了 - 这并不罕见，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But the death of a crewman-- - Regulations, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你船上的计算机记录能为你提供证词吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The extracts from your ship's computer log confirming this sworn deposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克呼叫进取号 - 舰桥收到，请说，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to Enterprise. - Bridge here. Go ahead, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克和计算机记录的数据在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Mr. Spock with that computer log extract?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他10分钟前应该就在那里了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, he should've been there ten minutes ago, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 寇克，完毕 - 很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk, out. - It's a great pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,军队无法失去像芬尼少校这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The service can't afford to lose men like Lieutenant Commander Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解，但也得等到最后一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I agree. I waited until the last possible moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当时红色警报已拉响，风暴愈演愈烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were on red alert. The storm got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不弃舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to jettison the pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么晚才到，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What took you so long, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我相信我… - 把它给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I believe I-- - I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 詹姆 - 原来你在这啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jame. - There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想再多看你一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just wanted one more look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个杀了我父亲的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man who killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,事情不是这样的，他是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not so. He was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友？你这辈子都在厌恶他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your friend? You hated him all your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你杀他的原因，你这个凶手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's why you killed him. You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个凶手，你这个凶手！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You murderer! You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，麻烦请你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, would you please...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼小姐，请跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Finney, come with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你是在红色警报拉响后才弃舱的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you say you jettisoned the pod after the red alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你这有我的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have my sworn deposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，舰长，我必须假定你在故意作伪证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then, captain, I must presume you have committed wilful perjury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这份计算机的记录显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This extract from your computer log says you jettisoned the pod
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在红色警报拉响前弃舱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before going to red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Consider yourself confined to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,官方调查后会确定是否需要最高军事法庭介入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An official enquiry will determine if a general court-martial is in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00DA4E&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：madscientist 傻得雷\N校对：诸星龟龟{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二十集\N军事法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2948.5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2948.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰进取号依旧停留在11号星际基地周围的轨道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starship Enterprise remains in orbit around Starbase 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的维修工作正在进行中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Full repairs in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我被强制留在11号星际基地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have been ordered to stand by on Starbase 11
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,直到有关芬尼少校死亡的调查结果出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until the enquiry into the death of Lieutenant Commander Finney can be conducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我对调查结果充满自信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am confident of the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂摩西，自那次火山探险后就再没见过你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Timothy, haven't seen you since the Vulcanian expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看，我们军官学校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I see our graduating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业班的学生也在场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}class from the academy is well represented.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,克里根，泰勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Corrigan. Teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干得怎样，麦克？ - 一般般，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How you doing, Mike? - I'll get by, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解为了维修你得暂留在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand you're laying over for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大项目？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Big job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就几天 - 然后就走了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Couple of days. - Be moving out then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这么希望我走？ - 哦，我只是想知道要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- In a hurry to see me go? - Oh, I just wondered how long
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你才会有一名新的记录官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it would take you to get a new records officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以说得再清楚点 - 我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You can talk plainer than that. - I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我刚才已把重点说出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I think the point's been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 本是我们的朋友 - 好了，吉姆，走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ben was a friend of ours. - Come on, Jim, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不，继续说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, go on, finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,本是你们的朋友，然后…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben was a friend of yours, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我洗耳恭听 - 你为什么不告诉我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm waiting to hear the rest. - Why don't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什么才是重点？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would be the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已做了决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've already made up your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有任何疑虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you have any doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定事关进取号的詹姆士·寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that was indeed Captain James Kirk of the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，你是他的朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I know. Are you a friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在这段艰苦的时期，是他为数不多的朋友之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In these trying times, one of the few.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伦纳德·麦考伊医生，你呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Leonard McCoy, and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利尔·肖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Areel Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是他的一位老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm a friend too. An old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我所有的老朋友看起来都像个医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of my old friends look like doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的老朋友看起来都像你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All of his look like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，你不如和我喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you might as well join me for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,随着调查的进行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With this enquiry coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他将需要所有他能交到的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he's going to need all the friends he can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,记录：调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Recording: enquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当事人：詹姆士·T·寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Matter: Captain Kirk, James T.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,内容：本杰明·芬尼少校的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Subject: circumstances of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡情形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Finney, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这份调查将决定是否对寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This enquiry to determine whether a general court-martial
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,召集最高军事法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}should be convened against Captain Kirk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,以伪证罪和渎职罪对其指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on charges of perjury and culpable negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,从你和芬尼少校的关系开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's begin with your relationship with Commander Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他很久了吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You knew him for a long time, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，在我还是一名学生时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, he was an instructor at the academy when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那当辅导员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a midshipman, but that didn't stand in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但这并不妨碍我们之间的友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of our beginning a close friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他的女儿詹姆，昨晚在这的那位，就是以我的名字取名的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His daughter Jame, who was here last night, was named after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道你们之间曾发生过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's common knowledge that something happened to your friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是秘密，几年后我们被派到同一艘飞船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's no secret. We were assigned to the same ship some years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有次我替他值班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I relieved him on watch once
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发现原子物质堆的控制电路开启了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and found a circuit open to the atomic matter piles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这本应处于关闭状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that should've been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再过五分钟整艘飞船就会被炸毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another five minutes, could have blown up the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,请说出飞船名称\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ship's nomenclature. specify.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,联合共和国号，编号1371\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}United Starship Republic, number 1371.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我关了开关并将此事记录了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I closed the switch and logged the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他遭到了斥责并被列入升职名单的末尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He drew a reprimand and was sent to the bottom of the promotion list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以他因此责怪你？ - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And he blamed you for that? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他在军官学校担任辅导员的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He had been at the academy for an unusually long time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,异常漫长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as an instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,导致他很晚才被任命到飞船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As a result, he was late in being assigned to a starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他感觉这在他的档案里看起来很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The delay, he felt, looked bad on his record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他认为我的所作所为使他陷入更为糟糕的境地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My action, he believed, made things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,注记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,追加有关芬尼少校的工作记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Service record of Commander Finney to be appended this enquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,记录生成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来详细谈谈那次风暴吧，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, let's get into the specifics of the storm, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,气象扫描仪显示离子风暴就在正前方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Weather scan indicated an ion storm dead ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我派芬尼去了吊舱 - 为什么是芬尼？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I sent Finney into the pod. - Why Finney?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恰好轮到他执勤 - 如果他想责怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He was top of the duty roster. - If he blamed--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他也许会责怪我，因为他从未驾驶过飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He may have blamed me that he never commanded a ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会因为谁责怪我而改变分工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I don't assign jobs on the basis of who blames me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到芬尼了，我便叫他去了吊舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was Finney's turn, and I assigned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他刚到达吊舱…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He had just checked in with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们就撞上了风暴的前沿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...from the pod when we hit the leading edge of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始情况并不糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not too bad at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我拉响了黄色警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I signalled a yellow alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但接着气压值，变异数，应力值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then we began encountering pressure, variance, stress,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,由于风暴的影响突然上升到7级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}force seven, the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我最终拉响了红色警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I finally signalled a red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼知道他大概只有几秒的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Finney knew he had a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也尽可能多给他几秒钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gave him those seconds and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然，这几秒完全不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, apparently, it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么，舰长，你船上计算机的自动记录显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then why, captain, does the computer log from your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在你弃舱时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}made automatically at the time, indicate that you were still on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只是拉响了黄色警报而不是红色警报？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}yellow alert when you jettisoned, and not on red?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 肯定是什么地方出问题了 - 看起来貌似是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- There's been a mistake. - It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机会出错吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could the computer be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生正在验算结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock is running a survey right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但这几乎不可能出错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the odds are next to impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,停止记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, look, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很少有人能像我俩一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not one man in a million could do what you and I have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Command a starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都要做出上百个决策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A hundred decisions a day, hundreds of lives
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,数以百计的生命取决于你正确的决策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}staked on you making every one of them right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经累了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're played out, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 筋疲力竭了 - 这就是你的看法？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Exhausted. - Is that the way you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意合作，我就将这样汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the way my report will read, if you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,身体垮了，甚至精神都崩溃了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Physical breakdown. Possibly even mental collapse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许 - 我会承认有人死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Possibly. - I'd be admitting that a man died--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也别承认，什么都别说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Admit nothing. Say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我们把事实就此掩盖吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me bury the matter here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从未有过星舰舰长受审，我不希望你成为第一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No starship captain has ever stood trial before, and I don't want you to be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的怀疑正确，我会感到内疚，我理应受到惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If what you suspect is true, I'm guilty. I should be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在为军队考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm thinking of the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会抹黑它的 - 通过什么手段，斯通准将？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I won't have it smeared-- - By what, Commodore Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,通过一名明显的伪证者，他掩盖了自己的错误判断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By an evident perjurer who is either covering up his bad judgement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 自己的懦弱或是其他更糟的 - 到此为止，先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- his cowardice or something worse. - That's as far as you go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你当时我就在舰桥上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm telling you I was there, on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我清楚发生了什么，我知道我做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what happened. I know what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就在记录里，计算机是不会撒谎的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's in the transcript, and computer transcripts don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你，你要么接受永久地面调派\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm telling you, either you accept a permanent ground assignment or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the whole disciplinary weight of Starfleet Command
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 星舰总部的纪律制裁吧 - 现在我们就是这么做的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- will light right on your neck. - So that's the way we do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,让事实掩盖，连我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sweep it under the rug and me along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你休想，我要找出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not on your life. I intend to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你将遭到法庭的起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you draw a general court.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,起诉？我强烈要求，现在就起诉我，斯通准将，就是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Draw it? I demand it. And right now, Commodore Stone. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2948.9\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2948.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,组成军事法庭委员会的成员们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The officers who will comprise my court-martial board
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,正前往11号星际基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are proceeding to starbase 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，进取号的维修工作已接近尾声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meanwhile, repairs on the Enterprise are almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Areel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生说你在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy said you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我本该通过空气就能察觉到，如静电般\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have felt it in the air, like static electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,奉承使你无处不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Flattery will get you everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,已经…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样已经多久了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,4年7个月零几天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Four years, seven months and an odd number of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没有刻意去计时 - 你看起里还是那么的美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Not that I'm counting. - You look marvellous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点都没变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但你变了，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things have changed for you, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你听说了，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, you've heard about that, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是军法官办公室的一名律师，还记得吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a lawyer in the Judge Advocate's office, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得，不提了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember. Let's forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们错过了很长时间，要尽力弥补\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a lot of lost time to make up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它看得很轻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're taking it very lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个无辜男人的信心 - 是这样吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The confidence of an innocent man. - Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,传闻可不是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not what the rumours indicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，不要三句不离本行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, let's not talk shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，这会毁了你的，你会接受建议吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, this could ruin you. Will you take some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远都无法说服你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never could talk you into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, fire away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官的立案基础\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The prosecution will build its case on the basis of Kirk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是寇克与计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}versus the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的律师想要对此辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, if your attorney tries to defend on that basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你是没有机会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you won't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的选择吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What other choice is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这取决于你的律师，所以他得足够的优秀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that's up to your attorney, and that's why he's got to be a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许，你能办到？ - 不，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You, perhaps? - No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很忙 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm busy. - Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这般优秀的女性是有能力同时处理两个案件的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a girl with your ability should be able to handle two cases at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，严肃点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身份不一般，你是一舰之长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not an ordinary human. You're a starship captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你正陷入丑门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you've stepped into scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会放过任何能拉你下台的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's any way they can do it, they'll slap you down
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是为了维护军队的利益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hard and permanently for the good of the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有给我任何的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You still haven't made any recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,塞缪尔·T·科格利律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Samuel T. Cogley, attorney at law.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人能够救你，就是他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If anyone can save you, he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他会去拜访你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll be paying you a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉姆，我必须走了 - 艾利尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jim, I've got to go. - Areel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉我你是怎么得到这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You still haven't told me how you know so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有关检察官如何行动的信息的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about what the prosecution's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为，吉姆·寇克，我的旧爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because, Jim Kirk, my dear old love...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那名检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I am the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须尽我所能将你狠狠的拉下台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I have to do my very best to have you slapped down hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,让你可耻地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}broken out of the service,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,离开军队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是寇克吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是些什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现我们得共处一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I figured we'd be spending some time together
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我搬了过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望没有挤到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hope I'm not crowding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，你不喜欢书吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the matter, don't you like books?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我很喜欢，不过电脑占地更少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I like them fine, but a computer takes less space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A computer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我从办公室带了台过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got one of these in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,里面储存了所有的案例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Contains all the precedents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,涵盖了过去到现在所有最出色的法律决策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A synthesis of all the great legal decisions written throughout time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不用它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我有自己的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got my own system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这些书，年轻人，书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Books, young man, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万的书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thousands of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果时间充裕，我会给你看些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lf time wasn't so important, I'd show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的图书馆，成千上万本书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My library. Thousands of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到底有什么用？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would be the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是法律的所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is where the law is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那种均匀化、巴氏消毒式、合成类…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not in that homogenised, pasteurised, synthesised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你想了解法律吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want to know the law? The ancient concepts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用其特有语言诉说的古老概念？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in their own language? Learn the intent of the men
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,了解制定者的意图？从摩西到阿尔法3号的法庭？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who wrote them? From Moses to the Tribunal of Alpha III?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都在这些书里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你要么是逃离监护人的强迫症疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to be either an obsessive crackpot who's escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就是塞缪尔·T·科格利律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from his keeper or Samuel T. Cogley, attorney at law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都被你说对了，需要律师吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're right on both counts. Need a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭现在正式开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This court is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我已任命以下人员为该庭审判员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have appointed, as members of this court...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太空司令部代表林斯特罗姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Space Command Representative Lindstrom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰舰长考茨基和香德拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Starship Captains Krasnovsky and Chandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长，请注意一个事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk, I direct your attention to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你认为上述人员在此次事件上对你持有偏见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you have a right to ask for substitute officers if you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你有权要求替换审判员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that any of these named harbour prejudiced attitudes to your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没任何异议，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no objection, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否同意肖上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And do you consent to the service of Lieutenant Shaw
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,作为这次的检察官，以及我作为法官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as prosecuting officer, and to myself as president of the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就绪，书记员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,指控：重大过失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charge: culpable negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,详述：星历2945.7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Specification: In that, on stardate 2945.7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长詹姆士·T·寇克由于疏忽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by such negligence, Captain Kirk, James T.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,导致记录官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did cause loss of life to wit, the life of records officer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,本杰明·芬尼少校死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Finney, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对于上诉控告，有何辩解？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To all recorded charges and specifications, what is the plea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不承认有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,继续，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Proceed, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请史波克先生陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I call Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克：编号S 179-276 SP\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock: serial number S 179-276 SP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,头衔：少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Service rank: lieutenant commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,职位：大副兼科学官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Position: first officer, science officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当前任职处：联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Current Assignment: USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,荣誉：瓦肯科学荣誉勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commendations: Vulcanian Scientific Legion of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,勇气奖：两次被星舰总部授勋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Awards of valour: twice decorated by starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，作为大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, as a first officer you know a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定对计算机相当了解，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about computers, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know all about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机是有可能发生故障的，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is possible for a computer to malfunction, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否知道进取号的计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know of any malfunction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,曾出现过故障导致不准确的情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which has caused an inaccuracy in the Enterprise computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的回答是基于本次审讯前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That answer is based on your mechanical survey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被告下令进行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the Enterprise computer, ordered by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号计算机机械调查，对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the defendant prior to this trial, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，星历…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, the stardate--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此，计算机还是不准确的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the computer is inaccurate, nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这样说？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,记录显示弃舱按钮是在红色警报拉响前被按下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It reports that the jettison button was pressed before the red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说，关于寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In other words, it reports that Captain Kirk
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,应对紧急情况的报告是不存在的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was reacting to an extreme emergency that did not then exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你当时在场亲眼看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Were you watching him the exact moment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他按下弃舱按钮了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he pressed the jettison button?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我当时无暇顾及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I was occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船已进入黄色预警状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship was already on yellow alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那这份记录你为何还能提出异议？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then how can you dispute the finding of the log?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有异议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not dispute it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想说这记录有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I merely state that it is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么这样说？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On what do you base that statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他是…  - 请给出证据，不要凭空猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He is in--  - Please instruct the witness, not to speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我也算半个瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am half Vulcanian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人是不会凭空猜测的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vulcanians do not speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是通过纯粹的逻辑进行说明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I speak from pure logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我让锤子在有重力的星球上下落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I let go of a hammer on a planet that has a positive gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不必看也知道它会下落，事实上，它已经落地了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need not see it fall to know that it has, in fact, fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不认为这能说明什么 - 先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I do not see what that has-- - Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,人类和无生命体有某些共同的特点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}human beings have characteristics just as inanimate objects do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长是不可能出于恐慌或恶意才这样做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is impossible for Captain Kirk to act out of panic or malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是他的本性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is not his nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是你个人的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我个人的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对此还有什么疑问吗，科格利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your witness, Mr. Cogley.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以归位了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在请进取号的人事官陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I now call the personnel officer for the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,头衔：少尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Service rank: ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,职位：人事官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Position: personnel officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当前任职处：联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Current assignment: USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在你担任进取号人事官期间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the course of your duties as personnel officer of the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该对船上所有人的工作记录都非常的熟悉吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you would be familiar with the service records of all aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,关于记录官芬尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With reference to Records Officer Finney
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他的工作记录中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was there in his service record
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有一份因未关闭电路而受到纪律处分的报告？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a report of disciplinary action for failure to close a circuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候的处分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was the charge, in that instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是依据替班人的日志记录吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}based upon a log entry by the officer who relieved him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And who was that officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·T·寇克少尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ensign James T. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请大声说，这里是法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Louder, please, for the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·T·寇克少尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ensign James T. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是坐在这个法庭里的寇克舰长吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now the Captain Kirk who sits in this courtroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有什么想问的吗，科格利先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you wish to cross-examine, Mr. Cogley?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以归位了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请麦考伊医生上来陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I now call Dr. McCoy to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,头衔：少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Service rank: lieutenant commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,职位：船医\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Position: ship's surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当前任职处：联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Current assignment: USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,荣誉：荣誉勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commendation: Legion of Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,勇气奖：由星际舰队医疗部授勋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Awards of valour: decorated by Starfleet surgeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，根据记录，你是心理学专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, you are, on the record, an expert in psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,特别擅长外太空漫长航程中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}especially space psychology patterns which develop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,产生于相近舱房的空间心理学模式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the close quarters of a ship during long voyages in deep space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对此我了解一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才也听到了你们人事官的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have just heard the testimony of your own personnel officer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是那时的寇克少尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that it was an action of the then Ensign Kirk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,造成了芬尼上尉记录上不可抹去的污点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which placed an un-erasable blot on the record
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,从心理上分析，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the then Lieutenant Finney. Psychologically, doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼上尉会不会因此责怪寇克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is it possible that Lieutenant Finney blamed Kirk for the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在接下来的几年，他可能会一直记恨着寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He could have hated Kirk, down through the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,得不到升迁，从未执掌过指挥棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}blamed him for being passed over for promotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,将这一切归咎于他，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}blamed him for never being given a command of his own, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可能 - 那么，让我们做个假设，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He could have. - Now, let us hypothesise, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以德报怨正常吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it normal for a person to return affection for hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不正常 - 对憎恨我们的人，我们是否倾向于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - Do we not tend to, at first, resent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始不满，然后极其厌恶？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then actively dislike the person who hates us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，我不太明白你的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait a minute, I don't quite follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,假设下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hypothetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:21:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,史密斯舰长是否会开始厌恶琼斯少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would not Captain Smith begin to hate Lieutenant Commander Jones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他得知琼斯少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}once he learned that Lieutenant Commander Jones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌、憎恶他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hated and detested him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我觉得可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yes, I suppose it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我问你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可不可能寇克舰长意识到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is it not possible that Captain Kirk became aware
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼少校对他的仇恨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of Lieutenant Commander Finney's hatred toward him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许，甚至是无心地开始回敬了呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and perhaps, even involuntarily, began to reciprocate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,以正常人来看，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any normal human, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不是那种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he's not that kind of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上是否可能，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it theoretically possible, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,该你了，科格利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your witness, Mr. Cogley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以退下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经听取了三位证人的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you have listened to testimony from three witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次你都没有利用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and in neither instance have you availed yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你的反诘问权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of your right to cross-examine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否放弃这个权利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you abrogated that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阁下，事实上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, sir, the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直忍着等热身运动结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been holding back till we get this preliminary business out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想提请寇克舰长上庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to call Captain Kirk to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·T·寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}James T. Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,编号SC 937-0176 CEC\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Serial number SC 937-0176 CEC.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,头衔：舰长 职位：星舰指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Service rank: captain. Position: starship command.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当前分配：联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Current assignment: USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,荣誉：阿克萨那和平行动棕榈叶奖章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commendations: Palm Leaf of Axanar Peace Mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,格兰凯特战术奖章，特等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Grankite Order of Tactics, Class of Excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,普伦特斯绶带，一等及二等——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prentares Ribbon of Commendation, Classes First and Second--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,庭上，请允许我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May it please the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭同意检察官请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Court recognises counsel for the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官承认寇克舰长的卓越履历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The prosecution concedes the inestimable record of Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想阻碍前进的车轮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't want to slow the wheels of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但另一方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想让这些车轮恣意匆匆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't want those wheels to run over my client
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,碾过我的委托人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in their unbridled haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:22:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,勇气奖：荣誉勋章，多枚银质棕榈勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Awards of valour: Medal of Honor, silver Palm with Cluster,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,星际舰队英勇卓越表彰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starfleet Citation for Conspicuous Gallantry,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡拉盖特勋章 - 停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Karagite Order of-- - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想碍太多事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't wanna slow things up too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那么舰长，不管这些机器说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, captain, despite what these machines indicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在你弃舱之前，真的已经红色警报了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was there indeed a red alert before you jettisoned the pod?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir, there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们谈谈吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please tell us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，我无法理解计算机提取出来的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Firstly, I am at a loss to explain the errors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,会出现错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the extract from the computer log.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到了离子风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were in an ion storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个庭上的每个人都明白它的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone here in this court knows the dangers involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我在指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,决定是我做出的，而非其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The decisions were mine, no one else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,预谋的罪名指向我，但没有预谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Charges of malice have been raised. There was no malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼少校是我舰上的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Commander Finney was a member of my crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正是如此待他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's exactly the way he was treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人认为我在舰桥上慌张了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has been suggested that I panicked on the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过早地抛弃了隔舱，事实不是那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and jettisoned the ion pod prematurely. That is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也听到了我履历里的一些细节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have heard some of the details of my record.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不是我遇到的第一次险情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This was not my first crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是九牛一毛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was one of many.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}During it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我所作所为是我的经验和训练所要求的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did what my experience and training required me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我以适当的次序采取了适当的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took the proper steps in the proper order.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我正是在该做的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did exactly what had to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,做了该做的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}exactly when it should have been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.17,0:24:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了正确的事情，但你下次还会这么做吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did the right thing, but would you do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.17,0:24:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是在同样的情况下…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Given the same circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.68,0:24:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,…我会毫不犹豫地再做一次同样的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I would do the same thing without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我采取的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because the steps I took,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和行动的次序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the order I took them,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.27,0:24:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,都是绝对必要的，如果我要救我的星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were absolutely necessary if I were to save my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而没有任何事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.86,0:24:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,比我的星舰更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is more important than my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.79,0:25:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到你了，肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your witness, Miss Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.50,0:25:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官并不想侮慢这位先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The prosecution does not wish to dishonour this man
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.88,0:25:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实就是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but facts are facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.51,0:25:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要提请庭上和寇克舰长注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must invite the attention of the court and Captain Kirk
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.49,0:25:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从进取号电脑记录里提取出的视频资料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to this visual extract from the Enterprise computer log.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.31,0:25:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,播放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Playback.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.73,0:25:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们即将看到的正是离子风暴期间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you are about to see is precisely what took place
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.15,0:25:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号舰桥上发生的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the Enterprise bridge during the ion storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,气象报告离子风暴即将到来，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meteorology reports ion storm upcoming, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.37,0:25:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要有人去隔舱读取读数，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll need somebody in the pod for readings, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.74,0:25:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 执勤表上第一位是芬尼先生 - 派他去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Finney is top of duty roster. - Post him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.66,0:25:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上尉 - 请注意，芬尼少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Lieutenant. - Attention, Commander Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.71,0:25:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请到隔舱报到读取离子板上的读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report to pod for reading on ionplates.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:26:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收到 - 人员到岗，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Message received. - Officer posted, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.43,0:26:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备警戒状态，史波克 - 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Stand by on alert status, Mr. Spock. - Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.81,0:26:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接近离子风暴，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approaching ion storm, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曲速1级，汉森 - 曲速1级，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Warp factor 1, Mr. Hansen. - Warp 1, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.57,0:26:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,倒退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.28,0:26:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.45,0:26:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放大仪表板，继续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go forward with magnification on the panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.50,0:26:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,重力控制切换到电池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gravity control switching to batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.25,0:26:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Freeze that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.21,0:26:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长现在发出了黄色警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk is now signalling a yellow alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.38,0:26:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,继续，标准视图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go forward, normal view.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.89,0:26:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 隔舱呼叫，长官 - 接进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Call from the pod, sir. - Tie in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是芬尼，舰长，正在读取离子读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Finney here, captain. Ion readings in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.68,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点，本，我可能要上红色警报了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make it fast, Ben. I may have to go to red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.77,0:26:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.94,0:27:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保持航向，汉森 - 遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hold your course, Mr. Hansen. - Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.74,0:27:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,横向振动，二级，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lateral vibrations, force two, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.95,0:27:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三级 - 轮机舱，然后离子隔舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Force three. - Engineering, then ion pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.50,0:27:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.00,0:27:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 轮机舱 - 加三分之一推力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Engineering. - One-third more thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.29,0:27:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,运转中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Working.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.67,0:27:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,离子隔舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ion pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.17,0:27:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随时准备离开，本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to get out of there, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.55,0:27:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,五级，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Force five, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,保持平稳，汉森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steady as she goes, Mr. Hansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.47,0:27:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Freeze that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.90,0:27:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,庭上注意到的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the court will notice
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,记录很明白地显示了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the log plainly shows
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.20,0:27:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,被告的手指按着投弃的按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the defendant's finger pressing the jettison button.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.19,0:27:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而仪表盘上显示的是黄色警报，而非红色警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The condition signal reads yellow alert, not red alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.40,0:27:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黄色警报，明白无误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but simply yellow alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.45,0:27:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,载有芬尼少校的隔舱被抛弃时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the pod containing Lieutenant Commander Finney was jettisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急情况并未发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the emergency did not as yet exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.55,0:28:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但事情不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's not the way it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.50,0:28:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2949.9\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2949.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.08,0:28:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,呈给最高军事法庭的视频资料证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The evidence presented by the visual playback to my general court-martial
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.80,0:28:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶，我觉得连我的律师都开始怀疑我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was damning. I suspect even my attorney has begun to doubt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机不会撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Computers don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.14,0:28:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就是说我撒谎了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you suggesting that I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.97,0:28:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说你可能的确有失误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm suggesting that maybe you did have a lapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.47,0:28:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是可能的，在你所受的压力下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was possible, you know, with the strain you were under.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.73,0:28:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有时间来修改抗辩，我可以让你脱身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's still time to change our plea. I could get you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,两天前，我还会把赌注全都押在自己的判断上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two days ago, I'd have staked anything on my judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.36,0:28:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你赌了，你的职业生涯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did. Your professional career.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.67,0:28:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一生都在训练做那样的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I spent my whole life training for decisions just like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.16,0:28:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,穷其一生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.33,0:28:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可不可能那时候…？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it possible that when the moment came...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.46,0:29:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.26,0:29:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.80,0:29:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以抽身，如果愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can pull out if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.09,0:29:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无处可逃啊，除非回法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no place to go, except back to court
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.72,0:29:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听取判决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and hear the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.81,0:29:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是寇克 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.60,0:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我对计算机进行了事无巨细的全面体检\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have run a complete megalite survey on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.15,0:29:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我来宣布你的发现吧，什么都没发现，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll tell you what you found. Nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.19,0:29:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,您的声音很苦，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sound bitter, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.78,0:29:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还没苦到不懂得谢你的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not bitter enough to forget to thank you for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.19,0:29:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,进一步的指示？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Further instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.60,0:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.12,0:29:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切没有想象的那么糟，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not all bad, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.11,0:29:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以在象棋上击败下一任舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may be able to beat your next captain at chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.51,0:29:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克，挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.80,0:29:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.05,0:29:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jame.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.80,0:29:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是芬尼的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Finney's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.59,0:29:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 芬尼小姐 -科格利律师，你必须得阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Miss Finney. - Mr. Cogley, you've got to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.18,0:29:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让他接受地面任务吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make him take a ground assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.43,0:29:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到这并不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I realise it wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.41,0:29:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再捣乱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't make any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.14,0:30:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让他修改抗辩吧 - 太迟了，詹姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Make him change his plea. - It's too late for that, Jame.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.86,0:30:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我很高兴你不再把发生的一切归咎于我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I'm glad you don't blame me anymore for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.19,0:30:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那天晚上我太沮丧了，对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just so upset that night. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别多说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.31,0:30:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我必须得说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.20,0:30:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未意识到你和爸爸以前是多么亲密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never realised how close you and Dad had been
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.74,0:30:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我读到他写过的一些信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until I read through some of the papers he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.24,0:30:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,给妈妈和我的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Letters to Mother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.46,0:30:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我怎么能那样想…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how I ever could have thought that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.09,0:30:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师，覆水难收，毁掉吉姆也无济于事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley, ruining Jim won't change what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.59,0:30:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的行为可圈可点，芬尼小姐，但非比寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's very commendable, Miss Finney, but most unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.13,0:30:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟，寇克舰长被指控导致你父亲的死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all, Captain Kirk is accused of causing your father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.06,0:30:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而证据也显示他有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the evidence would indicate his guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.38,0:30:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是为吉姆着想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just thinking of Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.01,0:30:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明白，非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, and I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.06,0:30:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了，你准备好了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to go and change. You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.76,0:30:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.77,0:30:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不过可能慢慢就准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I may be getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.49,0:30:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,飞象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bishop, half level right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.08,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，不是亲眼所见我是不会相信的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I had to see it to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.07,0:30:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说明一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.07,0:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就要腰斩舰长的职业生涯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're gonna lop off the captain's professional head,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.29,0:31:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却在这里和计算机下象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you're sitting here playing chess with a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.46,0:31:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.29,0:31:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你是我见过的最冷血的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, you're the most cold-blooded man I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.26,0:31:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，谢谢，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.55,0:31:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚赢了第四局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've just won my fourth game.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.93,0:31:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.98,0:31:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自己看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Observe for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.01,0:31:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,进車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rook to king's pawn four.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.52,0:31:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,飞象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bishop, half level right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.12,0:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是计算机的走法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, this is the computer's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.98,0:31:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.61,0:31:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.45,0:31:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,技术上而言，计算机没有缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mechanically, the computer is flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.74,0:31:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以从逻辑上来说，它举证舰长有罪是没有错的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Therefore, logically, its report of the captain's guilt is infallible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.58,0:31:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不能接受这种说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could not accept that, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.37,0:31:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就测试了程序库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you tested the programme bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.28,0:31:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对，几个月前我亲自设置了象棋程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly. I programmed it myself for chess some months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.05,0:31:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到的最好结果应该是平局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The best I should have been able to obtain was a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.55,0:31:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那你还坐在这里干嘛呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, why are you just sitting there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.09,0:31:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,传送室，准备，我们马上下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Transporter Room, stand by. We're beaming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Court is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.20,0:32:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在发布判决前，委员会欢迎提案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The board will entertain motions before delivering its verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.37,0:32:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Counsel for the prosecution?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大人，检察官完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, the prosecution rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.96,0:32:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被告律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Counsel for the defence?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.75,0:32:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.72,0:32:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…被告完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the defence rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.06,0:32:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.89,0:32:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.81,0:32:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.98,0:32:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚发现新的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some new evidence has just been brought to my attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求庭上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'd like to ask the court to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.03,0:32:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抗议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.12,0:32:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,被告律师对此案件已经完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Counsel for the defence has rested his case.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个证据是什么性质？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Of what nature is this evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.61,0:32:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告，只能展示给您，大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't tell you, I have to show you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:33:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师的表演天赋广为人知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley is well-known for his theatrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救一个无辜者的职业生涯是表演吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is saving an innocent man's career a theatric?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.41,0:33:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,律师请将评论传达给法官席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Counsels will kindly direct their remarks to the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.33,0:33:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,十分乐意，大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd be delighted to, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我可以谈谈人情了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now that I've got something human to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.71,0:33:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,权利，大人，人权，圣经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rights, sir, human rights. The Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.22,0:33:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,汉谟拉比法典，查士丁尼法典\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Code of Hammurabi and of Justinian.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.69,0:33:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大宪章，美国宪法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Magna Carta. The Constitution of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.47,0:33:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,火星殖民地的基本宣言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fundamental Declarations of the Martian Colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.83,0:33:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔法三号星章程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Statutes of Alpha III.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.94,0:33:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,…这些文件都在谈权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...these documents all speak of rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.86,0:33:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被告和同伴接受审理的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rights of the accused to a trial by his peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.11,0:33:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有律师为之辩护的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To be represented by counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.28,0:33:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,质证的权利，但最重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rights of cross-examination. But most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.79,0:33:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对抗不利证人的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the right to be confronted by the witnesses against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的委托人却没有享受这个权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A right to which my client has been denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.38,0:33:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人，这很荒谬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your Honour, that is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.04,0:33:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在庭上呈上证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We produced the witnesses in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.02,0:33:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我经验丰富的对手有机会观察他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My learned opponent had the opportunity to see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.49,0:33:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 盘诘他们—— - 还有一个证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- cross-examine them-- - All but one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.22,0:34:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对我委托人有毁灭性影响的证人并不是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The most devastating witness against my client is not a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.72,0:34:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.81,0:34:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一个信息系统，进取号的电脑记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An information system. The computer log of the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.71,0:34:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我提请休庭，去舰上重新开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I ask this court adjourn and reconvene aboard that vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.90,0:34:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我抗议，法官大人 - 我重复一遍，我在说权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I protest, Your Honour. - And I repeat. I speak of rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.99,0:34:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,机器没有权利，人必须有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A machine has none. A man must.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.45,0:34:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的委托人有权利面对原告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My client has the right to face his accuser.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.62,0:34:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不赋予他这个权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if you do not grant him that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.45,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就把我们拉低到机器的层级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you have brought us down to the level of the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.17,0:34:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,确实，你们已经将机器奉若神明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Indeed, you have elevated that machine above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.75,0:34:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要求我的请求得到同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I ask that my motion be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.42,0:34:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And more than that, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.34,0:34:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,以一个在机器阴影下枯萎的人类的名义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the name of a humanity fading in the shadow of the machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.10,0:34:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权要求，我必须要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I demand it. I demand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.51,0:34:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历2950.1\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 2950.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.22,0:34:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,经过适当考虑，最高军事法庭在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After due consideration, the general court-martial has reconvened
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.10,0:35:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号上重新开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}onboard the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.37,0:35:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢了电脑几局象棋，史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many games of chess did you win from the computer, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,总共五次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Five in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.35,0:35:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是非比寻常的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May that be considered unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.06,0:35:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.52,0:35:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.03,0:35:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己几个月前给电脑设置了象棋程序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I personally programmed the computer for chess months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.40,0:35:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我赋予了计算机相当于我自己的象棋水平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gave the machine an understanding of the game equal to my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.49,0:35:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机不可能出错，然后假定我也不出错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The computer cannot make an error, and assuming that I do not either,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.79,0:35:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,通常可以期待的最好结果就是僵局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the best that could normally be hoped for would be stalemate
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.58,0:35:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,接着僵局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}after stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.22,0:35:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然而我还是打败了计算机五次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And yet I beat the machine five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有人，不管是无意还是有意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone, either accidentally or deliberately,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.51,0:35:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,调整过程序，进而\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}adjusted the programming, and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.97,0:35:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,影响到计算机的内存库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the memory banks of that computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.81,0:35:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那这对我们看到的视频资料有影响吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could that have had an effect on the visual playback we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.48,0:35:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,反对，证人在做结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Object. The witness would be making a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.81,0:35:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,假设，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hypothetically, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.07,0:35:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,假设，肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hypothetically, Miss Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.45,0:36:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们所暗示的行为确实存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If what you suggest had been done,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这种能力也非常人所及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it would be beyond the capabilities of most men.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.66,0:36:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舰上的哪些人有这样的能力呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What man aboard ship would it not be beyond?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain, myself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.33,0:36:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有记录官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the records officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.84,0:36:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在，你们没有记录官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And at the moment, you have no records officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.01,0:36:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对，直到他消失之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative. Until he was lost
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.18,0:36:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的记录官一直是芬尼少校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our records officer was Lieutenant Commander Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.97,0:36:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.99,0:36:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能讲讲在风暴之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will you tell the steps you took to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.81,0:36:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你采取了哪些行动来寻找芬尼先生吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}find Mr. Finney after the storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.43,0:36:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我发起了一次一阶段搜寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I instituted a Phase 1 Search.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.77,0:36:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,描述一下一阶段搜寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Describe a Phase 1 Search.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.21,0:36:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是在舰上及周围寻找一位可能已受伤不能回应的人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a painstaking, thorough attempt, in and around the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.72,0:36:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种辛苦而彻底的尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to find a man who is presumably injured and unable to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.77,0:36:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是否假定这个人愿意被找到？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It presupposes, does it not, that a man wishes to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.49,0:36:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起没太听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.52,0:36:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你开始寻找一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you start a search for a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.04,0:36:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否会假定他想被找到？他没有藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you assume, don't you, that he wants to be found? He's not hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.88,0:36:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.83,0:36:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在这么大一艘舰船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On a ship of this size
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.17,0:36:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人能逃脱这样的搜寻吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}could a man evade such a search?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.09,0:37:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.47,0:37:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.18,0:37:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我主张，本·芬尼少校并没有死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I submit to you that Lieutenant Commander Ben Finney is not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.23,0:37:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,科格利律师，我们等着你在简报室做出的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Cogley, we are waiting for proof of the extraordinary statement
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.28,0:37:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个惊人陈述的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you made in the briefing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.48,0:37:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you shall have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.65,0:37:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先我需要法庭在一次实验中的合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But first I need the cooperation of this court in conducting an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.70,0:37:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.68,0:37:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.70,0:37:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为了这次实验之便，有必要让全体人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For the purposes of this experiment, it will be necessary for all personnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.08,0:37:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除了法庭成员和指挥人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}except for members of the court and the command crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.58,0:37:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,离开舰船，我命令其他人都去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to leave the ship. I am ordering all others to report
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.50,0:37:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 传送室报到 - 包括我，大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to the Transporter Room. - Including myself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.84,0:37:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不休庭，科格利律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This court is by no means adjourned, Mr. Cogley.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.95,0:37:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在地上有个差事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have an errand ashore of vital importance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.05,0:37:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对这次法庭极其重要，我会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the purpose of this court, and I will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.69,0:37:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.68,0:37:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，舰上有发动机人员吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, are you maintaining an engine crew aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.76,0:37:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的脉冲引擎已经关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our impulse engines have been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.39,0:37:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会依靠动量保持轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll maintain orbit by momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.06,0:37:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道什么时候开始衰变呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when the orbit begins to decay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.94,0:37:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望能早在那之前就结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We hope to be finished long before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.36,0:38:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.55,0:38:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.78,0:38:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，这个计算机有听觉感应器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, this computer has an auditory sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.54,0:38:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上，它可以听到声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It can, in effect, hear sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.21,0:38:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要安装扩爆器，我们就可以提升其性能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By installing a booster, we can increase that capability
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.67,0:38:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呈现一到四级的功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the order of one to the fourth power.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.42,0:38:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,计算机应该能将这艘舰上的每一个声音呈现给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The computer should be able to bring us every sound occurring on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,全体人员都已遵照命令离开舰船，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All personnel have left the ship as ordered, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.76,0:38:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.39,0:38:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.53,0:38:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,声音调小点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turn it down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.58,0:38:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，这声音是舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, that sound is caused by the heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.17,0:38:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的心跳声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of all the people onboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.46,0:38:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,会用这个消声器来遮盖每个人的心跳声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will use this white-sound device to mask out each person's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.51,0:39:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们听到的声音里就不会有那声音了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}heartbeat so that it will be eliminated from the sounds we are hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.14,0:39:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.23,0:39:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.21,0:39:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最后，是我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And lastly, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.17,0:39:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人都消了，除了传送室的工作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's all of us, except the crewman in the Transporter Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.55,0:39:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，消掉他的心跳声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, eliminate his heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.55,0:39:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是所有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That accounts for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.91,0:40:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,芬尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.09,0:40:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,定位这声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Localise that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.80,0:40:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,B甲板，轮机室区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}B Deck. In or near Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.53,0:40:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁B甲板，18-Y到23-D区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seal off B Deck, sections 18-Y through 23-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.69,0:40:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以芬尼还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So Finney is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.83,0:40:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.53,0:40:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,准将，这是我的私事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commodore, this is my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.33,0:40:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没人离开舰桥，我会十分感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would appreciate it if no one left the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.20,0:41:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,塞缪尔·科格利去地上接詹姆·芬尼上船了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam Cogley had gone ashore to bring Jame Finney onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.17,0:41:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都觉得詹姆在的话，处理芬尼会更容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We both felt that Jame's presence would make Finney easier to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.29,0:41:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果芬尼真的还活着的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the event Finney really were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.63,0:41:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.35,0:41:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,本·芬尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.56,0:41:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，有异动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, encountering variance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.62,0:41:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抵消 - 什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Compensate. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.44,0:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道开始衰变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The orbit is beginning to decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.48,0:41:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,本，你在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.08,0:41:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.79,0:41:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,无话可说么，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing to say, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.01,0:41:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.01,0:41:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己的职业生涯得到拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean you're relieved
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.66,0:41:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你可以如释重负了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because you think your career is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.39,0:41:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.19,0:42:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.69,0:42:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,本，还来得及，我们可以帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben, it's not too late. We can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.36,0:42:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你一直以来帮我那样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like you helped me all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.21,0:42:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把我踩在脚下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kept me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.20,0:42:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抢走了我的指挥棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Robbed me of my own command.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.83,0:42:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个好长官，和你旗鼓相当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a good officer. As good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.16,0:42:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我观察了你好些年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've watched you for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.62,0:42:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄舰长寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The great Captain Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.68,0:42:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们指示你对我动手脚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They told you to do it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.54,0:42:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都阴谋陷害我，你们毁了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You all conspired against me. You ruined me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.01,0:42:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不能再继续了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you won't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.23,0:42:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放下，本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put the phaser down, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.15,0:42:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀你的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I wouldn't kill you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:42:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己的死对我来说一文不值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your own death would mean too little to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.24,0:42:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的舰船——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But your ship--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.80,0:43:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的舰船怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about my ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.99,0:43:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它死了，我杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's dead. I've killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.75,0:43:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我破坏了你们的首要供能电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I tapped out your primary energy circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.80,0:43:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我们的轨道状况怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock. What's our orbit status?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.92,0:43:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 衰变中，舰长 - 二级异动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Decaying, captain. - Variance at second level
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.09,0:43:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恶化异常迅速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}depreciating unusually fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们断电了，我也对这船知根知底\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're out of power. I know this ship too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.27,0:43:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号本该是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Enterprise should've been mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.21,0:43:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你从我这里夺走了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You kept me from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.81,0:43:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.48,0:43:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,为何要杀害无辜的人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why kill innocent people?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.67,0:43:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,无辜？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.24,0:43:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当官的，绅士们，舰长们，所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Officers and gentlemen, captains all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.99,0:43:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是没有芬尼，他很久很久以前的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except for Finney, and his one mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.54,0:43:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一个错误，他们就是念念不忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a long time ago, but they don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.92,0:43:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我记录了那个错误，本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I logged the mistake, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怪我吧，不要怪他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blame me, not them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.46,0:43:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们有责任，所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But they are to blame. All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.46,0:43:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个好长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was a good officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.97,0:43:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.64,0:44:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,对这项事业，我比任何人都热爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I loved the service more than any man ever dared.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.31,0:44:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我们时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.31,0:44:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，请你们马上到传送室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, if you'll please hurry to the Transporter Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.81,0:44:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，法庭还没有得出判决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, the court has not yet reached a verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.07,0:44:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会听完这个证人的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will hear this witness out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.69,0:44:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.49,0:44:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还来得及，还可以帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not too late. You can be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.33,0:44:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你杀了那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you kill all those people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.69,0:44:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不可以？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.04,0:44:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们杀了我，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They killed me, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.71,0:44:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,公平交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a fair trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.33,0:44:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆也在这交易里吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is Jame included in that deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.09,0:44:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.88,0:44:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's onboard by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.84,0:44:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，她在舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, she's onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.73,0:44:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.10,0:44:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要把她带到这里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did you bring her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.86,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,筋疲力尽，啜泣不止的芬尼告诉了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beaten and sobbing, Finney told me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.90,0:45:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他破坏首要供能电路的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where he had sabotaged
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.02,0:45:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他造成的损害很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the prime energy circuits. The damage he had caused
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.57,0:45:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但尚能修补\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was considerable, but not irreparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.76,0:45:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,若一切顺利，我能在轨道完全衰变之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With luck, I would be able to effect repairs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.19,0:45:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,完成修复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before our orbit decayed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.66,0:46:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,电力恢复，史波克先生，14点，不断上涨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Power returning, Mr. Spock. Up 14 points and rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.95,0:46:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,激活左舷脉冲引擎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Activate port impulse engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.24,0:46:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三分之一电力 - 三分之一电力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- One-third power. - One-third power.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.63,0:46:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,异动减少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Variance fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.10,0:46:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orbit stabilising.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.20,0:47:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切安全，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All secure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.95,0:47:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,除非检察官反对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless the prosecution has an objection,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.00,0:47:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我宣布法庭解散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I rule this court be dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.54,0:47:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有意见，大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely no objection, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.69,0:47:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再见到你会是什么时候呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long will it be this time before I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.86,0:47:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冒着听似神秘主义者似的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the risk of sounding like a mystic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.27,0:47:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这得看星星的脸色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that depends on the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.74,0:47:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,塞缪尔·科格利让我带给你一份特殊礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam Cogley asked me to give you something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.78,0:47:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是首版藏本什么的，只是本书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not a first edition or anything, just a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.04,0:47:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这就足够让它独一无二了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam says that makes it special though.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.54,0:47:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没机会谢他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't have much of a chance to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.50,0:48:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他在忙着一个案子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's busy on a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.60,0:48:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为本·芬尼辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's defending Ben Finney.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.23,0:48:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他说会胜诉的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He says he'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.48,0:48:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我可毫不惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't be a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.89,0:48:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一个低级的上尉在一艘星舰的舰桥上亲吻舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think it would cause a complete breakdown of discipline
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.22,0:48:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这会导致纪律涣散吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if a lowly lieutenant kissed a starship captain on the bridge of his ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's try.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.91,0:48:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看，纪律严明，完好如初\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See, no change. Discipline goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.16,0:48:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号也一定会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And so must the Enterprise.
